[src:airdrie-north-lanarkshire/1-2-geo-4-p01] An Act to provide for the Charge of the Addition to the Public Funded Debt of the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Ireland, for the Service of the Year One thousand eight hundred and twenty one.
[src:airdrie-north-lanarkshire/1-2-geo-4-p01] An Act for better securing the Duties of Excise on Tobacco.
[src:airdrie-north-lanarkshire/1-2-geo-4-p01] An Act for repealing the Duties imposed on Husbandry Horses, and to make perpetual several Acts for reducing the Duties on certain Horses and Mules.
[src:airdrie-north-lanarkshire/1-2-geo-4-p01] An Act to empower the Commissioners in Great Britain for the Execution of several Acts for authorizing the Issue of Exchequer Bills for carrying on of Public Works and Fisheries, and Employment of the Poor, to extend the Time for the Payment of certain Advances under the said Acts.
[src:airdrie-north-lanarkshire/1-2-geo-4-p02] An Act to grant for the Term of Five Years additional Stamp Duties on certain Proceedings in the Courts of Law and to repeal certain other Stamp Duties in Ireland.
[src:airdrie-north-lanarkshire/1-2-geo-4-p02] An Act to continue several Acts for the Relief of Persons compounding for Assessed Taxes from an annual Assessment, for a further Term; and to amend the Acts relating to Assessments and Compositions of Assessed Taxes.
[src:airdrie-north-lanarkshire/1-2-geo-4-p02] An Act for the Conveyance, Surrender, and Assignment of Estates in Fee, for Lives, or Terms of Years, which shall be vested in Trust, or by way of Mortgage, in Idiots and Lunatics, not having been found such by Inquisition.
[src:airdrie-north-lanarkshire/1-2-geo-4-p02] relating to Bankrupts, as requires the Meetings under Commissions of Bankrupt to be holden in the Guildhall of the City of London; and for building Offices in the said City for the Meetings of the Com missioners; and for the more regular Transaction of Business in Bankruptcy.
